    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-text"
      }}>{`config/vector.toml
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`A full spec is located at `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`config/vector.spec.toml`}</inlineCode>{` and examples are
located in `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`config/vector/examples/*`}</inlineCode>{`. You can learn more about configuring
Vector in the `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/docs/setup/configuration/"
      }}>{`Configuration`}</a>{` section.`}</p>
    <h3 {...{
      "id": "data-directory"
    }}>{`Data Directory`}</h3>
    <p>{`We highly recommend creating a `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/docs/reference/global-options/#data_dir"
      }}>{`data directory`}</a>{`
that Vector can use:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`mkdir /var/lib/vector
`}</code></pre>
    <Alert type="warning" mdxType="Alert">
