        "href": "/docs/reference/global-options/#data_dir"
      }}><inlineCode parentName="a">{`data_dir`}</inlineCode>{` option`}</a>{` that
you can use to specify the path of your directory.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-toml",
        "metastring": "title=\"vector.toml\"",
        "title": "\"vector.toml\""
      }}>{`data_dir = "/var/lib/vector" # default
`}</code></pre>
    <h3 {...{
